OL,7,FA fire at a west London substation
OL,8,Fthat caused the shutdown of Heathrow
OL,9,FAirport was caused by a preventable
OL,10,Ftechnical fault that had been
OL,11,Fdiscovered seven years before but had
OL,12,Fnot been fixed, a report has found.
