OL,7,FOn Wednesday, Ofgem said it had opened
OL,8,Fan official enforcement investigation
OL,9,Finto National Grid Electricity
OL,10,FTransmission (NGET) based on the Neso
OL,11,Freview's findings.
OL,13,FThe fire on March 20 this year was
OL,14,Fcaused by a "catastrophic failure" in
OL,15,Fone of the transformers, "most likely
OL,16,Fcaused by moisture entering the
OL,17,Fbushing causing a short circuit",
OL,18,Fwhich ignited the oil, the Neso report
OL,19,Fsaid.
