OL,5,Cseven years ago
OL,7,FA review by the National Grid in 2022
OL,8,Ffound the fire suppression system at
OL,9,Fthe North Hyde site was "inoperable",
OL,10,Fwhile another assessment in July 2024
OL,11,Findicated the system was still "out of
OL,12,Fservice", the report said.
OL,14,FAll flights in and out Heathrow were
OL,15,Fhalted on March 20 after a fire
OL,16,Fknocked out the electricity substation
OL,17,Fin Hayes and did not resume until the
OL,18,Fevening of March 21.
OL,20,FMore than 270,000 air passenger
OL,21,Fjourneys were disrupted by the closure.
