OL,7,FThe electricity outage led to 71,655
OL,8,Fdomestic and commercial customers
OL,9,Flosing power and the "complete loss of
OL,10,Fsupplies" to part of Heathrow
OL,11,FAirport's internal electrical
OL,12,Fdistribution network, the report said.
OL,14,FAkshay Kaul, director general for
OL,15,Finfrastructure at Ofgem, said: "We
OL,16,Fexpect energy companies to properly
OL,17,Fmaintain their equipment and networks
OL,18,Fto prevent events like this happening.
