OL,7,F"Where there is evidence that they
OL,8,Fhave not, we will take action and hold
OL,9,Fcompanies fully to account."
OL,11,FThe Neso report, which was published
OL,12,Fon Wednesday and commissioned by
OL,13,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband, read:
OL,14,F"An elevated moisture reading in one
OL,15,Fof SGT3's (the transformer's) bushings
OL,16,Fhad been detected in oil samples taken
OL,17,Fin July 2018.
