OL,7,F"According to National Grid
OL,8,FElectricity Transmission's relevant
OL,9,Fguidance, such readings indicate 'an
OL,10,Fimminent fault and that the bushing
OL,11,Fshould be replaced'.
OL,13,F"While the reading was recorded in
OL,14,FNational Grid Electricity
OL,15,FTransmission's online system, the
OL,16,Fmitigations appropriate to its
OL,17,Fseverity were not actioned.
