OL,7,F"The controls in place were not
OL,8,Feffective and failed to identify
OL,9,Fsubsequently that action had not been
OL,10,Ftaken in relation to the elevated
OL,11,Fmoisture reading.
OL,13,F"This includes an opportunity in 2022
OL,14,Fwhen a decision was taken to defer
OL,15,Fbasic maintenance on SGT3. The issue
OL,16,Ftherefore went unaddressed."
