OL,7,FThe Neso review also found that the
OL,8,Fdesign and configuration of Heathrow's
OL,9,Finternal power network meant the loss
OL,10,Fof just one of its three supply points
OL,11,Fwould "result in the loss of power to
OL,12,Foperationally critical systems,
OL,13,Fleading to a suspension of operations
OL,14,Ffor a significant period".
