OL,7,FPlans were in place to respond to such
OL,8,Fan event, including the
OL,9,Freconfiguration of the network which
OL,10,Fwould take approximately 10 to 12
OL,11,Fhours, but the loss of a supply point
OL,12,Fwas "not assessed to be a likely
OL,13,Fscenario by Heathrow Airport Limited,
OL,14,Fdue to its expectation of the
OL,15,Fresilience of the wider network", the
OL,16,Freport said.
