OL,7,F"A combination of outdated regulation,
OL,8,Finadequate safety mechanisms and
OL,9,FNational Grid's failure to maintain
OL,10,Fits infrastructure led to this
OL,11,Fcatastrophic power outage.
OL,13,F"We expect National Grid to be
OL,14,Fcarefully considering what steps they
OL,15,Fcan take to ensure this isn't repeated.
OL,17,F"Our own review, led by former cabinet
OL,18,Fminister Ruth Kelly, identified key
OL,19,Fareas for improvement and work is
OL,20,Falready under way to implement all 28
OL,21,Frecommendations."
